      "content": "therapists dont get it. they just try to fix things that are fundamentally broken. i look at them and i just see how much better their lives would be if i wasnt in the picture. i'm just a constant source of stress and bad energy for them. it feels like the only way i could actually help them is if i just stopped being a burden.",
